@startuml
title Sequence Diagram - Detailed (Developers): Hospital Management Workflow

actor Patient as patient
actor Doctor as doctor
actor "Laboratory / Radiology Staff" as dept
actor Pharmacist as pharmacist
actor "Billing Officer" as billing

participant "Web / Mobile Portal" as portal
participant "Backend API" as api
database "Centralized Database" as db
participant "Notification Service" as notif

== Patient Registration / Login ==

patient -> portal : Register / Login
portal -> api : Send registration / login data
api -> db : Validate or create user account
db --> api : Validation / account result
api --> portal : Access result
portal --> patient : Display account access status

== Appointment Booking ==

patient -> portal : Book appointment
portal -> api : Submit appointment request
api -> db : Check doctor availability
db --> api : Availability status

alt Slot available
    api -> db : Save appointment
    db --> api : Appointment saved
    api -> notif : Send appointment confirmation
    notif --> patient : Appointment confirmation
    api --> portal : Booking successful
    portal --> patient : Show confirmed appointment
else Slot unavailable
    api --> portal : Suggest alternative time
    portal --> patient : Display unavailable slot message
end

== Doctor Reviews Appointment and Patient Record ==

doctor -> portal : View appointment schedule
portal -> api : Request schedule
api -> db : Fetch doctor schedule
db --> api : Schedule data
api --> portal : Return schedule
portal --> doctor : Display schedule

doctor -> portal : Open patient medical record
portal -> api : Request patient record
api -> db : Retrieve patient history
db --> api : Patient record data
api --> portal : Return medical record
portal --> doctor : Display patient record

doctor -> portal : Enter diagnosis
portal -> api : Submit diagnosis
api -> db : Update medical record
db --> api : Record updated
api --> portal : Update confirmed
portal --> doctor : Show update status

== Diagnostic Tests ==

alt Tests required
    doctor -> portal : Request lab / radiology tests
    portal -> api : Submit test request
    api -> db : Save diagnostic request
    db --> api : Request stored
    api --> portal : Request confirmed
    portal --> doctor : Show request status

    dept -> portal : Open assigned test request
    portal -> api : Request test details
    api -> db : Retrieve diagnostic request
    db --> api : Diagnostic request data
    api --> portal : Return request data
    portal --> dept : Display request details

    dept -> portal : Upload diagnostic results
    portal -> api : Submit test results
    api -> db : Save results to patient record
    db --> api : Results saved
    api -> notif : Notify doctor results are available
    notif --> doctor : Diagnostic results available
    api --> portal : Upload confirmed
    portal --> dept : Show upload status

    doctor -> portal : Review diagnostic results
    portal -> api : Request diagnostic results
    api -> db : Retrieve results
    db --> api : Results data
    api --> portal : Return results
    portal --> doctor : Display diagnostic results
else No tests required
    doctor -> portal : Continue treatment
end

== Prescription ==

doctor -> portal : Write prescription
portal -> api : Submit prescription
api -> db : Save prescription
db --> api : Prescription saved
api --> portal : Save confirmation
portal --> doctor : Show prescription status

pharmacist -> portal : View prescription
portal -> api : Request prescription
api -> db : Retrieve prescription
db --> api : Prescription data
api --> portal : Return prescription
portal --> pharmacist : Display prescription

pharmacist -> portal : Process / dispense medication
portal -> api : Update prescription status
api -> db : Save dispensing status
db --> api : Status updated
api --> portal : Update confirmed
portal --> pharmacist : Show dispensing status

== Billing ==

billing -> portal : Generate invoice
portal -> api : Request invoice generation
api -> db : Retrieve billable services
db --> api : Service details
api -> db : Save invoice
db --> api : Invoice saved
api --> portal : Invoice created
portal --> billing : Display invoice

billing -> portal : Record payment
portal -> api : Submit payment status
api -> db : Update billing record
db --> api : Payment recorded
api --> portal : Payment update confirmed
portal --> billing : Show payment status

== Patient Accesses Reports ==

patient -> portal : View medical report and billing details
portal -> api : Request reports and billing data
api -> db : Retrieve reports and invoice status
db --> api : Reports and billing data
api --> portal : Return requested data
portal --> patient : Display reports and billing details

@enduml